---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Me">
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto pt-8 pb-16 px-6">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
      
      <!-- Profile Photo (moved higher & bigger) -->
      <div class="flex justify-center md:justify-start -mt-8">
        <img 
          src="/jaa.png" 
          alt="Redžo Efendić" 
          class="w-48 h-48 md:w-64 md:h-64 rounded-full shadow-lg object-cover border-4 border-blue-500"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Intro Text -->
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">👋 Hi, I’m Redžo Efendić</h1>
        
        <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          I am a <strong>web developer</strong> from Bosnia and Herzegovina, passionate about building 
          clean, user-friendly, and efficient applications. My main focus is on 
          <strong>JavaScript, React, Node.js, and MongoDB</strong>, but I enjoy exploring new 
          technologies that help create better solutions.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          My journey started with curiosity for technology, and over time I turned that 
          curiosity into real projects. I’ve built applications ranging from simple 
          utilities to full-stack apps, including <em>Doctor Finder</em>, <em>Event Manager</em>, 
          and a <em>Recipes App</em> using React and Node.js. Through these projects, I learned 
          how to design databases, structure APIs, and create smooth user experiences.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Beyond coding, I enjoy <strong>teaching and mentoring</strong>. I’ve prepared 
          lessons for students, created educational 
          presentations, and discovered that helping others learn motivates me to keep 
          growing both as a developer and as a teacher.
        </p>

        <!-- What I’m Looking For -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">🎯 What I’m Looking For</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          I’m currently seeking a <strong>junior frontend</strong> or 
          <strong>full-stack developer</strong> role where I can grow my skills in 
          <em>React, Node.js, and MongoDB</em>, while contributing to impactful projects 
          in a collaborative team.
        </p>

        <!-- Languages -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">🌍 Languages</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-8 space-y-1">
          <li>Bosnian – Native</li>
          <li>English – Advanced</li>
          <li>German  – Beginner</li>
          <li>Turkish – Intermediate</li>
        </ul>

        <!-- Download CV -->
        <a 
          href="/Redzo-Efendic-CV.pdf" 
          download 
          class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-md hover:bg-blue-700 transition"
        >
          📄 Download My CV
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
       <!-- Skills -->
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Skills</h3>
      <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-gray-700 font-medium">
        <li>JavaScript (ES6+)</li>
        <li>React & Redux</li>
        <li>Node.js & Express</li>
        <li>MongoDB</li>
        <li>HTML5</li>
        <li>CSS3 / TailwindCSS</li>
        <li>Git & GitHub</li>
        <li>Astro</li>
      </ul>

    <!-- Timeline Section -->
    <div class="mt-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">📌 My Journey</h2>
      <div class="relative border-l-4 border-blue-500 ml-4 space-y-12">
        
        <div class="ml-6">
          <div class="absolute -left-5 top-0 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center">
            💼
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Encode IT Education & Mentorship</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">2023 – 2024</p>
          <p class="mt-2 leading-relaxed">
            Completed intensive training with mentors, building real-world projects using 
            JavaScript, Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and React. Hands-on learning with guidance from experienced mentors, focusing on 
            JavaScript, Node.js, and full-stack development.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="ml-6">
          <div class="absolute -left-5 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center">
            🤝
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">ZeForge Zenica Community</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">2024 - Ongoing</p>
          <p class="mt-2 leading-relaxed">
            Collaborated on apps such as a public transport solution and a website for the 
            mountain <em>Smetovi</em>, gaining teamwork and real project experience.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="ml-6">
          <div class="absolute -left-5 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center">
            📚
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Continuous Self-Learning</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Ongoing</p>
          <p class="mt-2 leading-relaxed">
            Strengthened my skills by building projects, exploring new technologies, and 
            contributing to community-driven work.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
